      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ON CASEY (8) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Finished second latest over 395m at Murray Bridge (22.33) in a Grade 5. Form here at the trip excellent including six wins. Rates highly and will give a great sight. RIPPIN' PEDRO (1) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.75 lengths win at this track in a handy 19.55. Has the coveted inside box and likes the trip. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Should feature again. TOWN STRANGER (4) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Gawler over 400m behind Carry On Kim (23.31) in a OPEN. Expected to give a good account. KICKER DUSTY (6) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
